data.name: label1.Text
data.value: How clever of you! You have crossed the whole country and come back to Dublin! How tricky these leprechauns are! They hid their treasure in the Phoenix Park where lots of deer live. The treasure has been in Dublin - the place where our journey began, but do not be upset! You had a great experience and learnt many things about Ireland. Enjoy your prize and relax now! Good Irish Luck!
